skdetail:

Invocation Name: candle farm
des:
Ride your virtual horse into our Candle Farm where you can learn how aromatherapy scents can add value to your personal space.
Candle Farm Ltd Co. is an aromatherapy candle company originating from Dunwoody, Georgia. We broker positive energy experiences through the power of aromatherapy!

You can say:
“Alexa, open Candle Farm”
“Alexa, ask Candle Farm about aromatherapy.”
“Alexa, ask Candle Farm about the benefits of aromatherapy.”

Visit our Amazon store: https://www.amazon.com/s?k=Candle+Farm 
Follow us on Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/CandleFarm
Questions or Comments: info@candlefarmorganics.com
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
